ent, contact our Technical Support team, or provide billing information.<br \/>\nLog Information. We automatically collect information about your use of our Services and your device, including your IP Address, device model, browser version, operating system type, operating system version, mobile network information, device settings, and software data.<br \/>\nLocation Information. We derive information about your general location (city, country) from your IP Address. We do not collect precise location data, such as GPS coordinates, that could be used to pinpoint your physical location.<br \/>\nInformation from Others. We collect information about you when we receive it from other users, third parties, and affiliates. For example, when you connect your account to third-party services or sign in using a third-party partner (like Google Play Game Services, iOS Game Center or Facebook), we collect information in accordance with the privacy policies and authorization procedures determined by those services.<\/p>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<h3>ADVERTISING AND ANALYTICS SERVICES PROVIDED BY OTHERS<\/h3>\n<p>We may allow others to provide analytics services and serve advertisements on our behalf across the internet and in applications. These entities may use cookies, web beacons, device identifiers and other technologies to collect information about your use of the Services and other websites and applications, including your IP address, web browser, mobile network information, pages viewed, time spent on pages or in apps, links clicked and conversion information. This information may be used by Elemento Dragons and others to, among other things, analyse and track data, determine the popularity of certain content, deliver advertising and content targeted to your interests on our Services and other websites and better understand your online activity. For a full list of the companies we partner with to show you interest-based ads, please visit <a href=\"https:\/\/www.arcube.com.np\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">www.arcube.com.np<\/a><\/p>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<h3>USE OF INFORMATION<\/h3>\n<p>We use the information we collect to deliver, personalize, and improve our Services. We also use the information we collect to:<\/p>\n<p>Personalize the Services and provide advertisements, content, or features that are targeted toward your interests;<br \/>\nSave and associate your activity across our Services and your different devices as well as associate any accounts you may use across our Services together. We may associate activity and accounts under a single user ID;<br \/>\nCarry out or support promotions;<br \/>\nCreate analytics and reports for external parties, including partners, publishers, advertisers, apps, third-parties and the public regarding the use of and trends within our Services and ads, including showing trends to partners regarding general preferences, the effectiveness of ads and information on user experiences; and<br \/>\nDetect and defend against fraudulent, abusive, or unlawful activity.<\/p>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<h3>SHARING OF INFORMATION<\/h3>\n<p>We share the information we collect within the Games we\u2019ve developed. We do NOT sell, license or share information that individually identifies our users with companies, organizations or individuals outside of Elemento Dragons unless one of the following circumstances applies:<\/p>\n<p>With Affiliated Brands. We share information within its affiliated brands.<br \/>\nWith Your Consent. We will share information with companies, organizations or individuals outside of Elemento Dragons when we have your consent to do so.<br \/>\nWith Service Providers. We provide user information to trusted partners who work on our behalf based on our instructions and in compliance with appropriate confidentiality measures.<br \/>\nFor Legal and Other Purposes. We may access, preserve, and disclose information to investigate, prevent, or take action in connection with: (i) legal process and legal requests; (ii) enforcement of our Terms of Service; (iii) claims that any content violates the rights of third parties; (iv) protecting the rights, property or personal safety of Game Circus, its users, or the public; (v) establishing or exercising our legal rights or defending against legal claims; or (vi) as otherwise required by law.<br \/>\nNew Ownership. If the ownership or control of all or part of Elemento Dragons or specific Services changes as a result of a merger, acquisition or sale of assets, we may transfer your information to the new owner.<\/p>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<h3>YOUR CHOICES<\/h3>\n<p>Accounts. In most cases, you can easily delete your data at any time by deleting the app and\/or resetting your Advertiser ID. We can no longer associate any stored data with you. If you have linked a social account (e.g. Facebook, GPGS or GameCenter), then you can unlink the app with those social providers to disassociate yourself with any stored data. If you do this, your unique username and game play may no longer be retrievable. If you have any further questions regarding remove of data, please contact <a href=\"mailto:info@elementodragons.io\">info@elementodragons.io<\/a><br \/>\nCookies. Most web browsers are set to accept cookies by default. If you prefer, you can usually choose to set your browser to remove or reject cookies; however, the Services may not function properly if you do so.<br \/>\nNotifications. You have the ability to turn application notifications on and off by adjusting the settings of your mobile device. If you wish to allow or discontinue receiving Push Notifications or Local Notification, please consult the settings on your mobile device.<\/p>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<h3>DATA RETENTION<\/h3>\n<p>We store the information we collect about you for as long as is necessary for the purpose(s) for which we originally collected it. We may retain certain information for legitimate business purposes or as required by law.<\/p>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<h3>PROTECTING CHILDREN\u2019S PRIVACY<\/h3>\n<p>Our Services are not intended for use by children. We do not knowingly collect, use, or share information from children under age 16. If you believe that your child may have provided us with personal information, please contact us at <a href=\"mailto:info@elementodragons.io\">info@elementodragons.io<\/a><\/p>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<h3>CONTACTS<\/h3>\n<p>If you have questions about data protection, or if you have any requests concerning your personal data, we encourage you to primarily contact us through the game, so we can reply to you more quickly.<br \/>\nName: Elemento Dragons<br \/>\nEmail: <a href=\"mailto:info@elementodragons.io\">info@elementodragons.io<\/a><\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Privacy Policy This Privacy Policy explains how information about you is collected, used and disclosed by Elemento Dragons. This Privacy Policy applies to our games, websites and related services, which we here collectively call the Service. We may periodically update this Privacy Policy by posting a new version on www.ElementoDragons.io. If we make any material [&hellip;]<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":2,"featured_media":0,"parent":0,"menu_order":0,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"closed","template":"default-page.php","meta":[],"yoast_head":"<!-- This site is optimized with the Yoast SEO plugin v19.14 - https:\/\/yoast.com\/wordpress\/plugins\/seo\/ -->\n<title>Privacy Policy | Elemento Dragons<\/title>\n<meta name=\"description\" content=\"Privacy Policy This Privacy Policy explains how information about you is collected, used and disclosed by Elemento Dragons. This Privacy Policy applies to\" \/>\n<meta name=\"robots\" content=\"index, follow, max-snippet:-1, max-image-preview:large, max-video-preview:-1\" \/>\n<link rel=\"canonical\" href=\"https:\/\/www.elementodragons.io\/privacy-policy\/\" \/>\n<meta property=\"og:locale\" content=\"en_US\" \/>\n<meta property=\"og:type\" content=\"article\" \/>\n<meta prope